{"tid":9923,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"無謂再關心你 我沒資格慰問你","createTime":"2016-11-28T17:53:29.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-25T11:38:21.000Z","uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d60ffc9693e6586a5e0de8e7948ef8e19b9995cd","tid":9923,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:53:29.000Z","msg":"無謂再騷擾你 我沒這塊厚面皮"},{"pid":"caed5cd8748c2aaebd8622d986711561e174a659","tid":9923,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:57:52.000Z","msg":"今天你能忘記 只得我懷念 多麼諷刺"},{"pid":"050ac4b78617f43080642a4b1d4ffea6dbcbd568","tid":9923,"uid":25933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T17:59:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38618496d38117dc9f939397f1e4e3c91ca6b378","tid":9923,"uid":26792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:01:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無謂再騷擾你 我沒這塊厚面皮</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無限次對不起 放在心裏等心死<br />\n難道我與他相比 尚有一線生機？<br />\n她起碼沒放棄"},{"pid":"57eb26e4236cebcb0369cd3390179a743c94183e","tid":9923,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:10:25.000Z","msg":"屌 收皮啦"},{"pid":"b7eec985c0721894642742388b4fa594027d30f8","tid":9923,"uid":29540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌 收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關你撚事 屌你老母"},{"pid":"da438952eb296b4195ff082f03d30ac111dc36d7","tid":9923,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:13:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌 收皮啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n關你撚事 屌你老母</blockquote><br />\n關你撚事 屌你老母"},{"pid":"363ff30d29ef7cc6f5b231a914ebd4a296945305","tid":9923,"uid":12851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:13:33.000Z","msg":"你的不安贏的你信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3e4e0305a207c6f76ed49e682a3dbfe3856f1a1","tid":9923,"uid":12851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:14:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你的不安贏的你信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n贏得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b623e1fea38cfbda19e207912d613c060a8b424e","tid":9923,"uid":8610,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T18:14:17.000Z","msg":"最後一次想念著你 最後一次再度記起"},{"pid":"4aa756b758ae8a63243176f7cf89537680c73e64","tid":9923,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:19:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自由是天多遠多高 不怕 自豪地飛出去吧 <br />\n那矛盾一生聽過了 算吧 算吧 忘記吧 <br />\n<br />\n聽聽滿山春風 柔和地說話 終於我明白 <br />\n看看滿野花草 纏綿地躺下 <br />\n記憶中你很重我得放下 <br />\n漫步我天下 現在我更快樂嗎 <br />\n<br />\n難道我存在是為了你 纏住你永遠都飛不起 <br />\n懷念夠下決心摘去你 終於我拍翼能飛 自由地飛 <br />\n尋覓我回頭便沒有你 雲霧裡飛躍嬉戲 <br />\n明白我存在是為了我 逼不得已決定離開你 <br />\n畢竟不停有好天氣 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聽聽故鄉的海 鯨魚在說話 形容我的家 <br />\n徘徊紅綠馬路 就讓我選擇 <br />\n要花盡力氣的愛太蒼白 <br />\n為何放不下 現在我更快樂嗎 <br />\n<br />\n難道我存在是為了你 纏住你永遠都飛不起 <br />\n懷念夠下決心摘去你 逼不得已決定離開你 <br />\n畢竟不能永久承受你 <br />\n<br />\n或者 也許 結果 不知道 <br />\n是否 究竟 最終 不知道 <br />\nDa di do Da di do Da di do <br />\nDa di do Da di do Da di do do di do <br />\n<br />\n難道我存在是為了你 纏住你永遠都飛不起 <br />\n懷念夠下決心摘去你 這刻我拍翼能飛 自由地飛一飛 <br />\n尋覓我回頭便沒有你 雲霧裡飛啊飛 <br />\n我明白到存在是為了我 <br />\n天空海闊決定離開你 再不提起 <br />\n飛出去 不相信明日無甜夢可期 不准放棄</span></span>"},{"pid":"ddb367f23ea25395881ba04d7c186bf171591f6a","tid":9923,"uid":35105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T07:20:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0527585c5b53be8d4fbca3532c5be233ca46cb32","tid":9923,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T11:38:21.000Z","msg":"push"}]}